-- China to encourage investments between China, Taiwan banks
-- 
-- Wed Mar 14, 2012 1:42am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/03/14/us-china-npc-wen-taiwan-idUSBRE82D07L20120314

 

 BEIJING  (Reuters) - China is willing to encourage mutual investments between Chinese and Taiwanese banks, Premier Wen Jiabao said on Wednesday. 
 He made the remarks during his annual news conference at the end of the annual meeting of parliament. (Reporting by Chris Buckley; Editing by  Ken Wills )